{"tid":1137401,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"IU捐款一億！","createTime":"2019-05-03T17:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T16:44:02.000Z","uid":34643,"like":135,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"22a7d28e2127a3d6ea731c44d8d10d2b062a1e14","tid":1137401,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"兒童節前夕捐款1億，光在「綠色雨傘兒童財團」就已捐款6億 <br />\nIU兒童節前夕為了弱勢兒童捐款1億韓元！ <br />\n<br />\n新聞翻譯：<br />\n歌手IU再次捐款一億。兒童保護代表性機關綠色雨傘兒童財團（會長李濟勛）5月3日表示「在兒童節前夕，歌手IU為扶持單親家庭和祖孫家庭兒童等經濟困難少數族群兒童，向財團捐款一億。」<br />\n兒童財團表示，「到了5月，貧困少數族群兒童會異常失落。IU一直以來對兒童十分關心，不為人知地進行了許多捐款，希望通過她的社會影響力讓捐助文化擴大到社會，讓需要幫助的孩子們過一個幸福的兒童節。」<br />\nIU從15年起向綠色雨傘兒童財團持續進行捐款，4月也為江原道山火受災兒童捐款1億。目前為止，已通過綠色雨傘兒童財團向兒童們提供了6億2千萬元的援助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1g2o8uky068j30ku112kfu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1g2o8uky068j30ku112kfu.jpg&h=8606ae40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1g2nh2d0fsyj311x1kwqft.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1g2nh2d0fsyj311x1kwqft.jpg&h=3711eb3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33800d4ff66af465e546fada796bdc9ef63aab9f","tid":1137401,"uid":143093,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"捐唔捐得俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我啱啱拎白卡"},{"pid":"eb90fed34365f36df20a4b3cb2aeb771bb7d8774","tid":1137401,"uid":26429,"like":115,"dislike":9,"score":106,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:28:10.000Z","msg":"雖然我幫唔到d咩<br />\n但我願意捐一億精比iu<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d48d203926938c12fff43fc8a2e111364b2e6f8","tid":1137401,"uid":7699,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"cite